real time  use case of environment variable in jenkins

Deploying to Different Environments:

first choice parameter is given and choices are production and stage user will input either of them then 

in pipeline deploy stage 

if [ "$ENVIRONMENT" == "production" ]; then
  # Deploy to production server
else
  # Deploy to staging server
fi

